<div class="mt-4">
    <h4>Form Introduction</h4>
    <p>Welcome to the student details form. Please fill in all the required fields to provide the necessary information about the student. Ensure that all details are accurate and up to date. If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team. Thank you for your cooperation.</p>

    <h5>Instructions for Filling Out the Form</h5>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>First Name:</strong> Enter the student's first name using alphabets only. Avoid using numbers or special characters.</li>
        <li><strong>Last Name:</strong> Enter the student's last name using alphabets only. Avoid using numbers or special characters.</li>
        <li><strong>Standard:</strong> Enter the current standard/class the student is enrolled in. Use numeric values (e.g., 5, 10).</li>
        <li><strong>Medium:</strong> Select the medium of instruction from the dropdown menu.</li>
        <li><strong>Date of Birth:</strong> Select the student's date of birth from the date picker. Ensure the format is correct (DD/MM/YYYY).</li>
        <li><strong>Mobile Number:</strong> Enter the student's mobile number. It should be a valid 10-digit number.</li>
        <li><strong>Alternative Mobile Number:</strong> Enter an alternative contact number. It should be a valid 10-digit number.</li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> Provide the complete address where the student resides. Include street, locality, etc.</li>
        <li><strong>City:</strong> Select the city from the dropdown menu. If your city is not listed, select the closest major city.</li>
        <li><strong>Region:</strong> Select the state/region from the dropdown menu.</li>
        <li><strong>Postal Code:</strong> Enter the postal code of the address. It should be a valid 6-digit number.</li>
    </ul>

    <h5>Writing Guidelines</h5>
    <ul>
        <li>Ensure all information provided is accurate and up to date.</li>
        <li>Double-check spelling and number entries to avoid errors.</li>
        <li>Use proper capitalization for names and addresses.</li>
        <li>Review the form before submitting to ensure all fields are completed.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you encounter any issues while filling out the form, feel free to contact our support team for assistance. We are here to help you ensure a smooth and efficient process. Thank you!</p>

</div>




